Package org.goplanit.assignment

Class TrafficAssignmentBuilder<T extends TrafficAssignment>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.goplanit.utils.builder.Builder<T>
      • org.goplanit.component.PlanitComponentBuilder<T>
        • org.goplanit.assignment.TrafficAssignmentBuilder<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EventBasedLtmTrafficAssignmentBuilder, LtmTrafficAssignmentBuilder, TraditionalStaticAssignmentBuilder
    public abstract class TrafficAssignmentBuilder<T extends TrafficAssignment>
extends PlanitComponentBuilder<T>
    All traffic assignment instances require a network, demand, and (equilibrium) smoothing procedure, all of which should be registered via this generic builder. Specific traffic assignment methods might require special builders derived from this builder
    Author:
    markr
